          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-70feec38c6e20dd8",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Head Office\n319 McRae Avenue 2nd Floor\nT. 1.866.560.0120 F./Tc. 1.866.560.0177 alternabank.ca\nTerms and Conditions:\nShort Term Deposits: Term Deposits of 364 days or less\n1. Minimum deposit of $500, $100 minimum deposit if under 19 years of age\n2. No withdrawal prior to maturity\n3. Simple interest calculated on the principal amount for the number of days in the term deposit and paid at maturity.\nLong Term Deposits: Term Deposits with a maturity date of 1 year (365 days) or greater\n1 Year Redeemable:\n1. Minimum deposit of $500, $100 minimum deposit if under 19 years of age\n2. Redemption available any time after 60 days\n3. Annual compound interest paid at maturity\n4. If term is redeemed anytime after 60 days prior to the 1 year anniversary, simple interest will be calculated on the\nprincipal amount for the number of days in the term and paid at redemption\n2 and 3 Year Flexi-Growth Term",
          "anchor_type": "page",
          "anchor_value": "page-1",
