          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-fb556e95770beabb",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "ulated on the\nprincipal amount for the number of days in the term and paid at redemption\n2 and 3 Year Flexi-Growth Term Deposits:\n1. Minimum deposit of $500, $100 minimum deposit if under 19 years of age\n2. Redemption available any time after 90 days. No partial redemptions permitted.\n3. Annual compound interest paid annually, at redemption or at maturity.\n4. Interest earned must be reinvested back into the term deposit.\n5. Interest payment is calculated based on the interest rate threshold applicable at time of redemption or maturity.\n6. If term is redeemed anytime after 90 days prior to the 1 year anniversary, simple interest will be calculated on the\nprincipal amount for the number of days in the term and paid at redemption.\n7. Not eligible to be held within a RIF plan. Upon conversion from an RSP to a RIF, the term will be redeemed and\nfunds will be deposited to a RIF cash account",
